      The system shall enforce configurable upper bounds on acceleration, deceleration, and maximum speed in the actuator commands so that motor commands remain within safe operating limits for the robot hardware, while ensuring that the chosen bounds allow the robot to achieve the mapping time constraint specified in the system configuration and remain compatible with the safety distance and emergency stop thresholds.
